                    </emph>
                    <emph>
                        <hi rend="background-color(#ffffff)">Hobbes </hi>
                    </emph>
                    <emph>
                        <hi rend="background-color(#ffffff)">(1588-1679) </hi>
                    </emph>
                    <emph>
                        <hi rend="background-color(#ffffff)">developed a complex relation with the Bible. Although he credited himself with the scientific foundation of politics, </hi>
                    </emph>
                    <emph>
                        <hi rend="background-color(#ffffff)">in </hi>
                    </emph>
                    <emph>
                        <hi rend="background-color(#ffffff)italic">The</hi>
