                    </emph>
                    <emph>
                        <hi rend="background-color(#ffffff)">), </hi>
                    </emph>
                    <emph>
                        <hi rend="background-color(#ffffff)">Hobbes </hi>
                    </emph>
                    <emph>
                        <hi rend="background-color(#ffffff)">made an increasing use of Scriptural evidence in support of his arguments. </hi>
                    </emph>
                    <emph>
                        <hi rend="background-color(#ffffff)">While</hi>
                    </emph>
