                    <emph>a growing number </emph>
                    <emph>of Scriptural</emph>
                    <emph>passages.</emph>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <emph>And y</emph>
                    <emph>et</emph>
                    <emph>, </emph>
                    <emph>t</emph>
                    <emph>he hundreds of Biblical quotations s</emph>
                    <emph>prinkled</emph>
