            <div type="div1" rend="DH-Heading1">
                <head>
                    <emph>
                        <hi rend="bold">O</hi>
                    </emph>
                    <emph>
                        <hi rend="bold">bjectives </hi>
                    </emph>
                </head>
                <p>
                    <emph>With this poster, we aim to showcase the benefits of a textometric approach to </emph>
