                    <emph> </emph>
                    <emph>take a fundamental step forward in accomplishing Jones’s research agenda. </emph>
                    <emph>However, </emph>
                    <emph>we </emph>
                    <emph>will </emph>
                    <emph>also </emph>
                    <emph>make a methodological contribution to</emph>
                    <emph>many historical humanities. T</emph>
                    <emph>he </emph>
                    <emph>textometric </emph>
                    <emph>analysis of Hobbes’s </emph>
                    <emph>exegetical practices</emph>
                    <emph> </emph>
                    <emph>will actually allow the development of a </emph>
                    <emph>computational approach to </emph>
                    <emph>the study of Biblical reception that could be applied to many modern textual corpora.</emph>
